var myname = "%";
Ti.API.info("test:" + myname);

This simple code shows wrong output on Android

Android
[INFO]  test:%%

iOS
[INFO]  test:%

---------------------
Reproduction procedure:

1.Create new project,
2.Paste this code below  in app.js 

var myname = "1%1";
Ti.API.info("test:" + myname);

var myname = "1\%1";
Ti.API.info("test:" + myname);

var myname = '1%1';
Ti.API.info("test:" + myname);

3:Build and run on android.

--------------------
Result

[INFO]  test:1%%1
